column1: These cols are required for the NL stats import.
=> the RNC_BSC and NCELL_RNC_BSC are optional, if they are included, their text is concatenated to the start of the cell ids
=> the CELL, NCELL, LAYER, NCELL_LAYER are all required.

=> the stats can be raw (in which case they will be converted to % of total atts per cell), or pre-processed (assumed to be already in the % atts of total cell atts).  Note: the atts can be mr reports or counter attempts or whatever.
=> is nbr, action, nl_size_new, dist are optional, click use if you have the data => these are good to have as they will be shown in the review dialog
